trans-unit.source: Creates and manages the channels that are used by clients to send messages to service endpoints.
Channel factories that implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> interface and their associated channels are generally used by the initiators of a communication pattern.
trans-unit.target: Canal fábricas que implementam o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> interface e seus canais associados são geralmente usados pelos iniciadores de um padrão de comunicação.

trans-unit.source: Listener factories that implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interface and their associated listeners provide the mechanisms with which channels are accepted for communications.
trans-unit.target: Fábricas de ouvinte que implementam o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interface e seus ouvintes associados fornecem os mecanismos com a qual os canais são aceitas para comunicação.

trans-unit.source: This class is not part of the channel model, but of the service model.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não é parte do modelo de canal, mas o modelo de serviço.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.CreateFactory%2A> method provides the means to create an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> for a service endpoint.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.CreateFactory%2A> método fornece os meios para criar um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> para um ponto de extremidade de serviço.

trans-unit.source: Use it to construct a client that hooks up to an interface contract on the service without using metadata or policy.
trans-unit.target: Usado para construir um cliente que se conecta a um contrato de interface do serviço sem o uso de metadados ou política.

trans-unit.source: Setting `ChannelFactory.Credentials.Windows.AllowedImpersonationLevel` to `TokenImpersonationLevel.Anonymous` always results in an anonymous logon regardless of impersonation level.
trans-unit.target: Configuração `ChannelFactory.Credentials.Windows.AllowedImpersonationLevel` para `TokenImpersonationLevel.Anonymous` sempre resulta em um logon anônimo, independentemente do nível de representação.

trans-unit.source: Special note for Managed C++ users deriving from this class:
trans-unit.target: Observação especial para usuários de C++ gerenciado derivar desta classe:

trans-unit.source: Put your cleanup code in (On)(Begin)Close (and/or OnAbort), not in a destructor.
trans-unit.target: Coloque a limpeza código em (On) (início) feche (e/ou OnAbort), não em um destruidor.

trans-unit.source: Avoid destructors; they cause the compiler to auto-generate <xref:System.IDisposable>.
trans-unit.target: Evite destruidores; eles fazer com que o compilador gere automaticamente <xref:System.IDisposable>.

trans-unit.source: Avoid non-reference members; they can cause the compiler to auto-generate <xref:System.IDisposable>.
trans-unit.target: Evitar membros de referência não; pode fazer com que o compilador gere automaticamente <xref:System.IDisposable>.

trans-unit.source: Avoid using a finalizer; but if you include one, you should suppress the build warning and call <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%28System.Object%29> and the finalizer itself from (On)(Begin)Close (and/or OnAbort) to emulate what would have been the auto-generated <xref:System.IDisposable> behavior.
trans-unit.target: Evite usar um finalizador; mas se você incluir um, você deve suprimir o aviso de compilação e chamar <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%28System.Object%29> e o finalizador automaticamente a partir (On) (início) feche (e/ou OnAbort) para emular o que seria o gerado automaticamente <xref:System.IDisposable> comportamento.

trans-unit.source: When adding behaviors programmatically, the behavior is added to the appropriate `Behaviors` property on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory> prior to the creation of any channel.
trans-unit.target: Ao adicionar programaticamente os comportamentos, o comportamento é adicionado ao apropriada `Behaviors` propriedade o <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory> antes da criação de qualquer canal.

trans-unit.source: See the example section for a code sample.
trans-unit.target: Consulte a seção de exemplo para obter um exemplo de código.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to insert programmatically a client behavior prior to the creation of the channel object by the factory.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como inserir programaticamente um comportamento do cliente antes da criação do objeto do canal pela fábrica.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory" /> class.
The name of the configuration file.
Initializes the channel factory with the behaviors provided by a specified configuration file and with those in the service endpoint of the channel factory.
If `configurationName` is `null`, only the behaviors specified in the service endpoint are loaded.
trans-unit.target: Se `configurationName` é `null`, somente os comportamentos especificados no ponto de extremidade de serviço são carregados.

trans-unit.source: If the wildcard, "*", is used, any endpoint configuration in the client configuration file is used, but only if there is precisely one.
trans-unit.target: Se o curinga "*", é usada, qualquer configuração de ponto de extremidade no arquivo de configuração do cliente é usado, mas somente se houver com precisão.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Do contrário, uma exceção será acionada.

trans-unit.source: Any other value for the `configurationName`, including the empty string "", matches the endpoint configuration with the same name.
trans-unit.target: Qualquer outro valor para o `configurationName`, incluindo a cadeia de caracteres vazia "", corresponde à configuração de ponto de extremidade com o mesmo nome.

trans-unit.source: See the [WCF Client Configuration](~/docs/framework/wcf/feature-details/client-configuration.md) topic for a discussion of the client configuration.
trans-unit.target: Consulte o [configuração de cliente do WCF](~/docs/framework/wcf/feature-details/client-configuration.md) tópico para obter uma discussão sobre a configuração do cliente.

trans-unit.source: The service endpoint of the channel factory is <see langword="null" />.
When implemented in a derived class, creates a description of the service endpoint associated with the channel factory.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint" /> associated with the channel factory.
Builds the channel factory for the current endpoint of the factory.
An <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory" /> for the endpoint of the current factory.

The endpoint of the service that the factory channels connect to is <see langword="null" /> or the endpoint's binding is <see langword="null" /> or is missing the element with the configuration name specified.
Gets the credentials used by clients to communicate a service endpoint over the channels produced by the factory.

The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials" /> used by clients if they are configured for the factory or if the endpoint is non-<see langword="null" /> and is in either the created or opening communication state; otherwise <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials" /> usado pelos clientes se eles estiverem configurados para a fábrica ou se o ponto de extremidade não for <see langword="null" /> e estiver no estado de comunicação criado ou aberto; caso contrário, <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> object is stored as a type of endpoint behavior and can be accessed through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> objeto é armazenado como um tipo de comportamento de ponto de extremidade e podem ser acessado por meio de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.OnOpened%2A> method initializes a read-only copy of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> object for the factory.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.OnOpened%2A> método inicializa uma cópia somente leitura do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> objeto de fábrica.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> object is used by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601> class (or a class that derives from this class) to create the proxy objects that can call services.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> objeto é usado pelo <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601> classe (ou uma classe derivada dessa classe) para criar os objetos de proxy que podem chamar serviços.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> object is also accessible through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.ClientCredentials%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> objeto também pode ser acessado por meio de <xref:System.ServiceModel.ClientBase%601.ClientCredentials%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Setting `ChannelFactory.Credentials.Windows.AllowedImpersonationLevel` to `TokenImpersonationLevel.Anonymous` always results in an anonymous logon regardless of impersonation level.
trans-unit.target: Configuração `ChannelFactory.Credentials.Windows.AllowedImpersonationLevel` para `TokenImpersonationLevel.Anonymous` sempre resulta em um logon anônimo, independentemente do nível de representação.

trans-unit.source: Gets the default interval of time provided for a close operation to complete.
The default <see cref="T:System.Timespan" /> that specifies how long the close operation has to complete before timing out.
trans-unit.target: O padrão <see cref="T:System.Timespan" /> que especifica quanto tempo a operação de fechamento deve concluir antes do tempo limite.

trans-unit.source: Gets the default service model close time-out if both the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Binding%2A> are `null`.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o serviço modelo fechar tempo limite padrão se o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Binding%2A> são `null`.

trans-unit.source: The default value for the service model close time-out is 1 minute.
trans-unit.target: O valor padrão para o limite de fechar de modelo de serviço é 1 minuto.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the value is set to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.CloseTimeout%2A> value associated with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, o valor é definido como o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.CloseTimeout%2A> valor associado com o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the default interval of time provided for an open operation to complete.
The default <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> that specifies how long the open operation has to complete before timing out.
trans-unit.target: O padrão <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> que especifica quanto tempo a operação de abertura deve concluir antes do tempo limite.

trans-unit.source: Gets the default service model open time-out if both the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Binding%2A> are `null`.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o serviço modelo aberto tempo limite padrão se o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Binding%2A> são `null`.

trans-unit.source: The default value for the service model open time-out is 1 minute.
trans-unit.target: O valor padrão para o tempo de limite serviço modelo aberto é 1 minuto.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the value is set to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.OpenTimeout%2A> value associated with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, o valor é definido como o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.OpenTimeout%2A> valor associado com o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the service endpoint to which the channels produced by the factory connect.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint" /> to which the channels produced by the factory connect.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint" /> ao qual os canais produzidos pela fábrica se conectam.

trans-unit.source: Opens the current channel factory if it is not yet opened.

Before opening the channel factory, checks that it is not <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState.Closed>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState.Closing>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState.Opened>.
trans-unit.target: Antes de abrir a fábrica de canais, verifica se ele não <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState.Closed>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState.Closing>, ou <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState.Opened>.

trans-unit.source: The current factory is either closing or closed and so cannot be opened.
The typed object for which the method is querying.
trans-unit.target: O objeto com tipo para o qual o método está consultando.

trans-unit.source: Returns the typed object requested, if present, from the appropriate layer in the channel stack, or <see langword="null" /> if not present.
The typed object <paramref name="T" /> requested if it is present or <see langword="null" /> if it is not.
Use this to retrieve capabilities, requirements and parameters from the channel stack.
trans-unit.target: Use isto para recuperar recursos, requisitos e parâmetros da pilha de canais.

trans-unit.source: If a channel factory supports returning the requested object, it returns it.
trans-unit.target: Se uma fábrica de canais suporta retornar o objeto solicitado, ele retorna.

trans-unit.source: If not, it delegates the call down to the next level in the stack.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, ela delega a chamada para o próximo nível na pilha.

trans-unit.source: If it gets to the bottom of the stack and no channel factory supported the requested object, then the method returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Se ele obtém a parte inferior da pilha de nenhuma fábrica de canais suporte para o objeto solicitado e o método retornará `null`.

trans-unit.source: `T` is typically some channel interface that the channel factory can support.
trans-unit.target: `T` é normalmente alguma interface de canal que pode dar suporte a fábrica de canais.

trans-unit.source: If, for example, `GetProperty<IChannelListener>` is called on a duplex channel factory, it returns the underlying listener.
trans-unit.target: Se, por exemplo, `GetProperty<IChannelListener>` é chamado em uma fábrica de canais duplex, ele retorna o ouvinte subjacente.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the service endpoint of the channel factory.
You must have an address to initialize an endpoint, but can have just the binding or configuration instead of the full endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Você deve ter um endereço para inicializar um ponto de extremidade, mas pode ter apenas a associação ou a configuração em vez do ponto de extremidade completa.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint" /> to initialize the channel factory with.
Initializes the service endpoint of the channel factory with a specified endpoint.
Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> if you have just the binding.
trans-unit.target: Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> se você tiver apenas a associação.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.String%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> if you have the configuration.
trans-unit.target: Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.String%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> se você tiver a configuração.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="endpoint" /> is <see langword="null" />.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding" /> with which to initialize the channel factory.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress" /> with which to initialize the channel factory.
Initializes the service endpoint of the channel factory with a specified binding and address.
Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.String%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> if you have the configuration.
trans-unit.target: Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.String%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> se você tiver a configuração.

trans-unit.source: The name of the configuration file used to initialize the channel factory.
Initializes the service endpoint of the channel factory with a specified address and configuration.
Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> if you have just the binding.
trans-unit.target: Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.InitializeEndpoint%28System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding%2CSystem.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> se você tiver apenas a associação.

trans-unit.source: Terminates the inner channel factory of the current channel factory.

The <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.OnAbort%2A> method is called on a factory after it transitions to the closing state if the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.CommunicationObject.Abort%2A> method is invoked.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.OnAbort%2A> método é chamado em uma fábrica depois que ele passa para o estado de fechamento, se o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.CommunicationObject.Abort%2A> método é invocado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> that specifies how long the operation has to complete before timing out.
The <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" /> delegate that receives the notification of the asynchronous operation completion.
An object, specified by the application, that contains state information associated with the asynchronous operation.
Begins an asynchronous close operation on the inner channel factory of the current channel factory that has a state object associated with it.
The <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous operation.
This method receives notification, through a callback, of the identity of the event handler for the operation.
trans-unit.target: Este método recebe notificação por meio de um retorno de chamada da identidade do manipulador de eventos para a operação.

trans-unit.source: The operation is not complete until either the asynchronous close on the inner channel factory returns or the time-out occurs.
trans-unit.target: A operação não é completa até que o fechamento assíncrono na fábrica de canais interna retorna ou o tempo limite ocorre.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> that specifies how long the operation has to complete before timing out.
The <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" /> delegate that receives the notification of the asynchronous operation completion.
An object, specified by the application, that contains state information associated with the asynchronous operation.
Begins an asynchronous open operation on the inner channel factory of the current channel factory that has a state object associated with it.
The <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous operation.
This method receives notification, through a callback, of the identity of the event handler for the operation.
trans-unit.target: Este método recebe notificação por meio de um retorno de chamada da identidade do manipulador de eventos para a operação.

trans-unit.source: The operation is not complete until either the asynchronous open on the inner channel factory returns or the time-out occurs.
trans-unit.target: A operação não é completa até que retorna a assíncrona abrir a fábrica interna de canais ou o tempo limite ocorre.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> that specifies how long the operation has to complete before timing out.
Calls close on the inner channel factory with a specified time-out for the completion of the operation.
The <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> returned by a call to the <see cref="M:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.OnBeginClose(System.TimeSpan,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> method.
Completes an asynchronous close operation on the inner channel factory of the current channel factory.
The <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> returned by a call to the <see cref="M:System.ServiceModel.ChannelFactory.OnBeginOpen(System.TimeSpan,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> method.
Completes an asynchronous open operation on the inner channel factory of the current channel factory.
The <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> that specifies how long the open operation has to complete before timing out.
Calls open on the inner channel factory of the current channel factory with a specified time-out for the completion of the operation.
The inner channel of the current channel is <see langword="null" />.
Initializes a read-only copy of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials" /> object for the channel factory.
Overrides and invokes the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.CommunicationObject.OnOpened%2A> method, which is called during the transition of an object into the opened state.
trans-unit.target: Substituições e invoca o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.CommunicationObject.OnOpened%2A> método, que é chamado durante a transição de um objeto no estado aberto.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> object is stored as a type of endpoint behavior and can be accessed through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> objeto é armazenado como um tipo de comportamento de ponto de extremidade e podem ser acessado por meio de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Builds the inner channel factory for the current channel.
The inner channel factory for the channel factory is <see langword="null" />.
Closes the current channel factory.
